item.title: CVE-2023-26153|2023-10-06T05:00:01.453Z -- n%2Fa -- geokit-rails
item.description: Versions of the package geokit-rails before 2.5.0 are vulnerable to Command Injection due to unsafe deserialisation of YAML within the 'geo_location' cookie. This issue can be exploited remotely via a malicious cookie value. **Note:** An attacker can use this vulnerability to execute commands on the host system.
